title: Episode 3 - Honest Reflection
itunes:title: Episode 3 - Honest Reflection
description:
Before we conquer our future goals we must first look back and do an honest reflection of how well we have done with past goals - where we have succeeded and where we have fallen short. In this episode, we will cover relationships, personal growth, spirituality, finances, and career goals.
